response.overview: Freddie Starr's Comedy Express moves along at high speed bringing you the best moments from the multi-talented Freddie Starr.  Watch the hilarious antics of Freddie's Show Biz Eleven. The team includes Max Wall, Norman Wisdom, Quasimodo, Ray Charles, Tarzan, Dracula - to name just a few!  Among the many clips is Freddie's very own impersonation of Elvis Presley, a couple of lively dance numbers and some of his memorable appearances in the Des O'Connor Show.  This specially compiled video contains fun, music and a large helping of laughter from the inimitable FREDDIE STARR.
response.title: Freddie Starr: The Comedy Express
